name: __ECommonUserAvailability
doc: Enum specifying the general availability of a feature or privilege, this combines information from multiple sources

Unknown: State is completely unknown and needs to be queried
NowAvailable: This feature is fully available for use right now
PossiblyAvailable: This might be available after the completion of normal login procedures
CurrentlyUnavailable: This feature is not available now because of something like network connectivity but may be available in the future
AlwaysUnavailable: This feature will never be available for the rest of this session due to hard account or platform restrictions
